==============================================================================
================================ DINKY THEME =================================
==============================================================================

This licenses file applies to the contents of the /dinky/ subfolder of
“gh-themes-magick”, as found in the project’s relative path:

    /gh-themes/dinky/

The contents of this folder are a derivative work of a third party theme:

-   “dinky” theme by Diana Mounter, CC-BY 3.0:
    https://github.com/jasonlong/cayman-theme

They also include additional files taken from the “highlight.js”
project/package:

-   “highlight.js” (c) 2006, Ivan Sagalaev, BSD-3-Clause License:
    https://highlightjs.org
-   “GitHub Gist” theme by Louis Barranqueiro:
    https://github.com/isagalaev/highlight.js/blob/master/src/styles/github-gist.css
    https://github.com/LouisBarranqueiro

Changes for adapation were carried out by Tristano Ajmone, maintainer of the
“gh-themes-magick” project. For more information on the changes introduced in
this derivative work, see the ‘CHANGELIST’ file.

